    "name": {
      "zh": "AR-15 Noveske KX3 5.56x45消焰器",
      "en": "AR-15 Noveske KX3 5.56x45 flash hider"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "KX3",
      "en": "KX3 556"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "Noveske KX3消焰器，也叫做“燃烧的猪”。这款消焰器通过增加向后的压力并向射手前方引导膛口爆震，从而增加AR-15枪族之中短枪管型号的可靠性。虽然起初是为短枪管AR-15设计的，但是它可以装在任何长度的枪管上并且已经被大规模的使用。KX3消焰器适用于有1/2x28膛口螺纹的5.56毫米枪管。\n",
      "en": "The Noveske KX3 Flash hider, aka the Burning Pig, is designed to increase reliability in short-barreled members of AR-15 family by increasing backpressure and directing the muzzle blast forward of the shooter. Although originally designed for short-barreled AR-15s, it will work on any barrel length and have since been introduced for a variety of mounts. This particular KX3 may be used on 5.56mm barrels with 1/2x28 threading."
    },
